1
00:01:08,200 --> 00:01:09,960
[Episode 10: Secret Love]

2
00:01:12,200 --> 00:01:14,840
Ren Xi Zhou definitely likes Zhong Yi.

3
00:01:14,840 --> 00:01:16,745
Who is Zhong Yi?

4
00:01:19,080 --> 00:01:20,480
He's so handsome!

5
00:01:20,480 --> 00:01:22,480
Wow. You're so popular.

6
00:01:22,480 --> 00:01:23,840
So?

7
00:01:23,840 --> 00:01:25,600
Why are you laughing?

8
00:01:25,600 --> 00:01:28,965
I mean, that's not a friend's act.

9
00:01:30,920 --> 00:01:33,520
What's the secret of your charm? Share with me.

10
00:01:33,520 --> 00:01:35,012
What is it?

11
00:01:35,719 --> 00:01:38,040
You're so long-winded. Let's go.

12
00:01:38,040 --> 00:01:40,335
He's so tall and handsome!

13
00:01:40,335 --> 00:01:41,200
Yeah.

14
00:01:41,200 --> 00:01:42,879
Let's play basketball later.

15
00:01:42,879 --> 00:01:44,336
Okay, let's go.

16
00:01:45,080 --> 00:01:46,599
What a big bow!

17
00:01:46,599 --> 00:01:48,880
Isn't she afraid of the headmaster?

18
00:01:48,880 --> 00:01:50,923
But she looks pretty good.

19
00:01:51,640 --> 00:01:54,154
Will I look good with a bow?

20
00:01:54,154 --> 00:01:55,399
No!

21
00:01:56,070 --> 00:01:57,326
Oh.

22
00:02:02,920 --> 00:02:04,443
Abandon.

23
00:02:04,443 --> 00:02:06,189
Abandon.

24
00:02:06,189 --> 00:02:07,632
Abandon.

25
00:02:08,450 --> 00:02:09,636
Abandon.

26
00:02:09,636 --> 00:02:11,160
So far?

27
00:02:11,160 --> 00:02:12,708
None of your business.

28
00:02:15,112 --> 00:02:17,520
Boys are all idiots.

29
00:02:17,520 --> 00:02:19,131
Idiots!

30
00:02:23,629 --> 00:02:25,047
Abandon.

31
00:02:25,985 --> 00:02:27,734
Abandon.

32
00:02:29,319 --> 00:02:30,911
- Good morning.
- Good morning.

33
00:02:47,141 --> 00:02:48,669
It's lip balm.

34
00:02:48,669 --> 00:02:50,509
My mom insisted I put it on.

35
00:02:52,680 --> 00:02:55,454
It's color-changing lip balm.

36
00:02:55,454 --> 00:02:57,065
No.

37
00:03:11,599 --> 00:03:13,191
Nice shot!

38
00:03:14,589 --> 00:03:15,940
What's up?

39
00:03:19,380 --> 00:03:20,760
Come on!

40
00:03:20,760 --> 00:03:22,882
- Pass, pass!
- Here!

41
00:03:23,590 --> 00:03:25,580
Some guys enjoy showing off so much.

42
00:03:25,580 --> 00:03:26,680
Nice!

43
00:03:26,680 --> 00:03:29,040
For the sports meeting,
they're just practicing.

44
00:03:29,040 --> 00:03:30,240
Nice shot, nice!

45
00:03:30,240 --> 00:03:32,119
Slow down.

46
00:03:33,665 --> 00:03:35,418
Cool!

47
00:03:36,018 --> 00:03:37,411
Cool!

48
00:03:38,120 --> 00:03:39,600
Nice shot!

49
00:03:39,600 --> 00:03:41,039
Okay, next.

50
00:03:41,039 --> 00:03:42,360
- Go for it!
- Lovesick again?

51
00:03:42,360 --> 00:03:45,227
Please! With me, please!

52
00:03:45,880 --> 00:03:47,280
Come on.

53
00:03:47,280 --> 00:03:48,970
Go, go, go!

54
00:03:48,970 --> 00:03:51,263
Senior, go!

55
00:03:51,850 --> 00:03:54,856
- Defend him!
- So handsome!

56
00:03:55,990 --> 00:03:57,655
- Nice shot!
- Pass.

57
00:03:58,294 --> 00:03:59,720
Nice shot!

58
00:03:59,720 --> 00:04:01,070
Go for it!

59
00:04:01,070 --> 00:04:02,080
Come.

60
00:04:02,080 --> 00:04:03,600
One more!

61
00:04:05,760 --> 00:04:07,570
Go, Senior!

62
00:04:07,570 --> 00:04:08,654
Defend!

63
00:04:08,654 --> 00:04:10,320
Nice!

64
00:04:10,320 --> 00:04:13,135
- Nice shot!
- Go, go!

65
00:04:15,360 --> 00:04:17,140
- Come.
- Go, Senior!

66
00:04:17,140 --> 00:04:19,600
Go, go, go! Go, Senior!

67
00:04:19,600 --> 00:04:21,730
But Ren Xi Zhou and Zhong Yi
certainly won't be lovers.

68
00:04:21,730 --> 00:04:22,734
- Go, Senior!
- Nice.

69
00:04:22,734 --> 00:04:23,900
Pass to him.

70
00:04:23,900 --> 00:04:25,398
- Heard me?
- Go!

71
00:04:25,990 --> 00:04:27,040
Who are you looking at?

72
00:04:27,040 --> 00:04:28,946
- Slow down.
- Pass.

73
00:04:29,880 --> 00:04:31,252
Ren Xi Zhou?

74
00:04:31,905 --> 00:04:34,160
- What? Oh.
- Go!

75
00:04:34,160 --> 00:04:35,959
- The moon.
- Nice shot!

76
00:04:35,959 --> 00:04:37,279
Tomorrow will be sunny.

77
00:04:37,279 --> 00:04:38,320
The moon?

78
00:04:38,320 --> 00:04:39,959
Isn't it the sun?

79
00:04:39,959 --> 00:04:41,704
You're right.

80
00:04:42,399 --> 00:04:43,866
It has a moon halo.

81
00:04:44,439 --> 00:04:46,450
Forget it. Shouldn't we do something?

82
00:04:46,450 --> 00:04:49,160
- Nice!
- Go, Senior!

83
00:04:49,160 --> 00:04:52,240
- How?
- Go, go, go!

84
00:04:52,240 --> 00:04:53,360
You're a good writer.

85
00:04:53,360 --> 00:04:55,279
Write a letter to report Zhong Yi's puppy love

86
00:04:55,279 --> 00:04:57,808
and put it into the suggestion box of Grade 11.

87
00:04:58,385 --> 00:05:01,160
If it works, Zhong Yi will be criticized,

88
00:05:01,160 --> 00:05:03,120
[Principal Mailbox]
and Ren Xi Zhou will be heartbroken.

89
00:05:03,120 --> 00:05:05,760
It can prevent them
from being affected by puppy love.

90
00:05:05,760 --> 00:05:07,534
It'll be a great deed!

91
00:05:12,680 --> 00:05:14,247
You're the junior.

92
00:05:15,313 --> 00:05:17,200
You know me?

93
00:05:17,200 --> 00:05:18,862
You're here to...

94
00:05:19,520 --> 00:05:21,020
Let's sit and talk.

95
00:05:21,020 --> 00:05:22,030
Okay.

96
00:05:22,639 --> 00:05:24,199
Next Friday,

97
00:05:24,199 --> 00:05:25,440
my staff and I will be

98
00:05:25,440 --> 00:05:26,759
on vacation in Nanwan.

99
00:05:26,759 --> 00:05:28,199
It's the tourist season,

100
00:05:28,199 --> 00:05:31,040
so few restaurants can provide group meals.

101
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:33,439
I've been driving around downtown.

102
00:05:33,439 --> 00:05:34,560
By coincidence,

103
00:05:34,560 --> 00:05:35,960
I found you here.

104
00:05:35,960 --> 00:05:38,160
You're in the right place!

105
00:05:38,160 --> 00:05:41,240
Please let me know
the duration and the group size.

106
00:05:41,240 --> 00:05:43,139
Including me,

107
00:05:43,760 --> 00:05:45,560
it's 87 people in total.

108
00:05:45,560 --> 00:05:47,040
Five days and four nights.

109
00:05:47,040 --> 00:05:48,920
Nighttime arrival, daytime departure.

110
00:05:48,920 --> 00:05:51,190
The budget for each meal is...

111
00:05:55,400 --> 00:05:56,840
Wipe with it.

112
00:05:56,840 --> 00:05:58,172
Thank you.

113
00:06:01,512 --> 00:06:03,280
How about we switch seats?

114
00:06:03,280 --> 00:06:04,760
It's fine, it's fine.

115
00:06:04,760 --> 00:06:06,080
I'm sorry, Mr. Zhong.

116
00:06:06,080 --> 00:06:07,600
Your handkerchief gets dirty. I'll wash...

117
00:06:07,600 --> 00:06:08,920
The budget is

118
00:06:08,920 --> 00:06:10,800
30 yuan per person for lunch,

119
00:06:10,800 --> 00:06:12,840
and 35 yuan for dinner.

120
00:06:12,840 --> 00:06:14,016
Okay.

121
00:06:15,680 --> 00:06:17,072
Let me check.

122
00:06:17,959 --> 00:06:19,318
Let me do it.

123
00:06:35,880 --> 00:06:38,704
It's fine. Just a bit windy.

124
00:06:41,659 --> 00:06:42,932
Oh,

125
00:06:43,720 --> 00:06:45,291
just call me Zhong Yi.

126
00:06:48,560 --> 00:06:50,639
The group meal is almost set.

127
00:06:50,639 --> 00:06:52,120
A deposit will be paid.

128
00:06:52,120 --> 00:06:54,920
We'll make a trial group meal next Friday.

129
00:06:54,920 --> 00:06:56,795
If he's satisfied, we'll serve for four days

130
00:06:56,795 --> 00:06:58,200
and receive the final payment.

131
00:06:58,200 --> 00:07:00,240
If not, no refund is needed.

132
00:07:00,240 --> 00:07:03,046
It'll be a tasting fee and compensation.

133
00:07:03,046 --> 00:07:04,808
You're amazing!

134
00:07:06,280 --> 00:07:07,560
But...

135
00:07:07,560 --> 00:07:09,520
we're short-staffed.

136
00:07:09,520 --> 00:07:11,364
We need to hire one.

137
00:07:11,364 --> 00:07:12,480
It's a peak season.

138
00:07:12,480 --> 00:07:14,170
Short-staffed everywhere.

139
00:07:14,170 --> 00:07:15,480
We missed the boat.

140
00:07:15,480 --> 00:07:17,035
Not sure if we can find.

141
00:07:17,600 --> 00:07:18,708
Me.

142
00:07:22,879 --> 00:07:24,129
It sounds so good.

143
00:07:24,129 --> 00:07:25,600
The sign holder needn't wear uniform

144
00:07:25,600 --> 00:07:27,079
and can be well-dressed.

145
00:07:27,079 --> 00:07:28,960
Actually, I'd love to go too. But I...

146
00:07:28,960 --> 00:07:30,969
Anyone else?

147
00:07:32,121 --> 00:07:33,320
Go.

148
00:07:33,320 --> 00:07:35,199
No, I can't.

149
00:07:35,199 --> 00:07:36,640
If I look eager,

150
00:07:36,640 --> 00:07:37,680
I'd be regarded

151
00:07:37,680 --> 00:07:39,319
as stealing the limelight,

152
00:07:39,319 --> 00:07:40,640
which feels embarrassing.

153
00:07:40,640 --> 00:07:41,966
So what?

154
00:07:47,880 --> 00:07:49,167
Idiot.

155
00:07:52,800 --> 00:07:53,806
[Recruitment]

156
00:07:54,960 --> 00:07:57,520
Aren't you busy flying around as an actor?

157
00:07:57,520 --> 00:07:58,942
Why are you back?

158
00:07:59,560 --> 00:08:01,360
And you, missy.

159
00:08:01,360 --> 00:08:02,852
You're no longer a painter?

160
00:08:03,454 --> 00:08:04,480
In a big project,

161
00:08:04,480 --> 00:08:06,320
I'll play a restaurant waiter.

162
00:08:06,320 --> 00:08:07,610
So I come back

163
00:08:07,610 --> 00:08:09,480
and experience the job before filming.

164
00:08:09,480 --> 00:08:11,120
I need materials for my illustrations

165
00:08:11,120 --> 00:08:12,920
in a restaurant management game.

166
00:08:12,920 --> 00:08:15,280
But we're hiring a temporary packer,

167
00:08:15,280 --> 00:08:17,399
not a waiter.

168
00:08:17,399 --> 00:08:20,000
Right. It's a... packer role.

169
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:22,587
It's a takeaway-themed game.

170
00:08:22,587 --> 00:08:24,280
By the way,

171
00:08:24,280 --> 00:08:26,959
meals are provided, right?

172
00:08:26,959 --> 00:08:29,080
Are you experienced in packing?

173
00:08:29,080 --> 00:08:30,334
I can learn.

174
00:08:30,334 --> 00:08:31,720
I'm a fast learner.

175
00:08:31,720 --> 00:08:34,240
I'm faster.
Seriously, I'd be a puppy if I lied.

176
00:08:34,240 --> 00:08:35,652
Bark twice.

177
00:08:38,618 --> 00:08:41,134
[Hongxia Diner]

178
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:45,280
You're a puppy.

179
00:08:45,280 --> 00:08:46,640
You laugh at me?

180
00:08:46,640 --> 00:08:48,039
So what if I laugh at you?

181
00:08:48,039 --> 00:08:50,880
I'm talking about you.

182
00:08:50,880 --> 00:08:52,387
Talking about you.

183
00:09:14,400 --> 00:09:15,849
I'm talking about you.

184
00:09:18,400 --> 00:09:19,729
Here, slowly.

185
00:09:21,720 --> 00:09:22,872
Okay.

186
00:09:23,560 --> 00:09:24,739
Okay.

187
00:09:31,000 --> 00:09:32,120
Thanks for your hard work.

188
00:09:32,120 --> 00:09:34,043
I've transferred the deposit to you.

189
00:09:34,043 --> 00:09:36,440
Call me anytime if you have questions.

190
00:09:36,440 --> 00:09:37,517
I will.

191
00:09:38,600 --> 00:09:40,080
Zhong Yi?

192
00:09:40,080 --> 00:09:42,080
What's going on with them?

193
00:09:42,680 --> 00:09:44,251
Mr. Zhong, wait.

194
00:09:44,960 --> 00:09:46,980
Here. Thank you.

195
00:09:49,693 --> 00:09:51,680
Something's up.

196
00:09:51,680 --> 00:09:53,563
It can't be.

197
00:09:54,399 --> 00:09:55,679
How about this?

198
00:09:55,679 --> 00:09:57,000
At 10 PM tonight,

199
00:09:57,000 --> 00:09:59,400
let's have a drink somewhere.

200
00:09:59,400 --> 00:10:01,080
Okay, I'll wait for your call.

201
00:10:01,080 --> 00:10:02,281
Bye.

202
00:10:09,320 --> 00:10:12,279
- You clap one, I clap one.
- You clap one, I clap one.

203
00:10:12,279 --> 00:10:15,039
You clap two, I clap two.

204
00:10:18,920 --> 00:10:20,033
I told you,

205
00:10:20,033 --> 00:10:21,480
it doesn't work if you come to me.

206
00:10:21,480 --> 00:10:23,365
If you want to audition, tell your agent

207
00:10:23,365 --> 00:10:25,208
to contact the casting director.

208
00:10:25,208 --> 00:10:26,240
By chance?

209
00:10:26,240 --> 00:10:27,430
No chance.

210
00:10:29,942 --> 00:10:31,360
You and Ren Xi Zhou...

211
00:10:31,360 --> 00:10:32,860
Just friends.

212
00:10:37,000 --> 00:10:40,120
Today I saw Ren Xi Zhou and Zhong Yi...

213
00:10:40,120 --> 00:10:42,002
Forget it. You go ahead.

214
00:10:52,600 --> 00:10:53,716
I'm leaving, Mr. Xiang.

215
00:10:53,716 --> 00:10:55,370
I'll be back tomorrow night.

216
00:10:59,640 --> 00:11:02,360
I just finished Episode 10

217
00:11:02,360 --> 00:11:04,115
and sent it to the editor-in-charge.

218
00:11:04,840 --> 00:11:06,241
So... congrats?

219
00:11:07,400 --> 00:11:09,920
You can continue with the topic.

220
00:11:09,920 --> 00:11:11,981
Ren Xi Zhou and Zhong Yi...

221
00:11:11,981 --> 00:11:13,330
Time to feed my pet.

222
00:11:13,330 --> 00:11:14,360
I can drive you home.

223
00:11:14,360 --> 00:11:15,840
And I'm hungry.

224
00:11:15,840 --> 00:11:17,302
It's on me.

225
00:11:18,588 --> 00:11:19,600
Are you in a hurry?

226
00:11:19,600 --> 00:11:20,861
No.

227
00:11:38,240 --> 00:11:39,600
Weren't you upset last week

228
00:11:39,600 --> 00:11:41,120
because you heard he was dating?

229
00:11:41,120 --> 00:11:42,639
It was a misunderstanding.

230
00:11:42,639 --> 00:11:46,320
Jiang He is his mom's sister's daughter.

231
00:11:46,320 --> 00:11:47,360
They're just close.

232
00:11:47,360 --> 00:11:50,400
His mom's sister's what?

233
00:11:50,400 --> 00:11:51,674
They're cousins.

234
00:11:52,280 --> 00:11:54,325
So it's not true...

235
00:12:20,039 --> 00:12:21,680
that they're reported as puppy love?

236
00:12:21,680 --> 00:12:23,279
It's true.

237
00:12:23,279 --> 00:12:24,960
Someone wrote a report letter.

238
00:12:24,960 --> 00:12:27,080
When called to the headmaster's office,

239
00:12:27,080 --> 00:12:29,080
they were amused.

240
00:12:29,080 --> 00:12:31,080
These people have nothing better to do.

241
00:12:31,080 --> 00:12:33,506
Yeah. And clueless.

242
00:12:37,400 --> 00:12:38,763
Not me.

243
00:12:38,763 --> 00:12:40,271
It was me.

244
00:12:46,600 --> 00:12:48,710
<i>Hey, what are you doing?</i>

245
00:12:50,040 --> 00:12:52,709
We had a deal. Why didn't you go?

246
00:12:53,400 --> 00:12:55,480
It's not good to make up stories.

247
00:12:56,727 --> 00:12:59,327
The headmaster asked me to promise.

248
00:13:00,007 --> 00:13:01,240
Promise what?

249
00:13:01,240 --> 00:13:03,600
I promise it's not nonsense.

250
00:13:03,600 --> 00:13:06,480
Predestined love is the best.

251
00:13:06,480 --> 00:13:08,340
Who'd know they will keep in touch

252
00:13:08,340 --> 00:13:09,962
and have a drink?

253
00:13:12,021 --> 00:13:14,725
He drives a pretty nice car.

254
00:13:15,800 --> 00:13:17,227
Hey, Nan Feng.

255
00:13:19,680 --> 00:13:20,800
Zhu Qiao Fei!

256
00:13:20,800 --> 00:13:22,470
We haven't seen each other
since high school graduation.

257
00:13:22,470 --> 00:13:24,237
Long time no see.

258
00:13:24,840 --> 00:13:27,360
Hey, how are your pal and his ex?

259
00:13:27,360 --> 00:13:29,461
Which pal? What ex?

260
00:13:30,240 --> 00:13:31,400
Free side dish.

261
00:13:31,400 --> 00:13:32,644
Enjoy.

262
00:13:38,480 --> 00:13:40,159
My pal heard that

263
00:13:40,159 --> 00:13:42,760
his ex seems to
have fallen for someone else recently.

264
00:13:42,760 --> 00:13:44,922
So he stopped contacting her.

265
00:13:46,000 --> 00:13:47,759
She contacts your pal

266
00:13:47,759 --> 00:13:49,701
and dates another man?

267
00:13:50,360 --> 00:13:51,601
No.

268
00:13:53,200 --> 00:13:55,137
He cares about her lately,

269
00:13:55,970 --> 00:13:57,440
but doesn't want

270
00:13:57,440 --> 00:13:59,156
to rekindle an old flame.

271
00:13:59,767 --> 00:14:01,080
So he said he was busy working

272
00:14:01,080 --> 00:14:02,919
and purposely distanced himself.

273
00:14:02,919 --> 00:14:04,200
Then it's not her fault.

274
00:14:04,200 --> 00:14:06,320
He didn't seize the opportunity.

275
00:14:06,320 --> 00:14:08,749
He's probably painfully regretting it.

276
00:14:08,749 --> 00:14:10,092
No.

277
00:14:10,899 --> 00:14:11,920
No past?

278
00:14:11,920 --> 00:14:13,219
No regret.

279
00:14:17,566 --> 00:14:19,320
Just an ex,

280
00:14:19,320 --> 00:14:20,630
not an enemy.

281
00:14:21,240 --> 00:14:23,929
One can still be a friend after a breakup.

282
00:14:28,080 --> 00:14:29,600
Isn't it good if a friend

283
00:14:29,600 --> 00:14:31,664
can be happy? Right?

284
00:14:33,040 --> 00:14:34,960
That's a big chili pepper.

285
00:14:34,960 --> 00:14:36,278
Aren't you choking?

286
00:14:42,120 --> 00:14:43,200
Go get water.

287
00:14:43,200 --> 00:14:44,639
- Which one?
- That one.

